  <brief_title>Adjuvant PEG Intron in Ulcerated Melanoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Adjuvant Pegylated-Interferon-alpha2b (SylatronTM) for 2 Years Versus Observation in Patients With an Ulcerated Primary Cutaneous Melanoma With T(2-4)bN0M0: a Randomized Phase III Trial of the EORTC Melanoma Group.</official_title>
